again.

00:15.949 --> 00:16.216 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All that and more
on tonight's
"PBS NewsHour."

00:16.250 --> 00:18.085 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
