rights office
said today the toll is even
higher when you

01:01.128 --> 01:02.996 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
count other factors.

01:03.030 --> 01:04.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RAVINA SHAMSADANI, Spokeswoman,
United Nations
High Commissioner for Human
Rights: It doesn't

01:04.898 --> 01:08.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
