for people
with disabilities, for the
elderly. So, this

01:18.612 --> 01:20.480 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
is really the tip of the
iceberg.

01:20.514 --> 01:26.053 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The U.N. agency
also said that
Islamic State militants are
holding some 3,500

01:26.086 --> 01:30.123 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Iraqis as slaves, many of them
women and children.

01:30.157 --> 01:35.462 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
In economic news, China
announced today that
its economy met fourth-quarter
projections,

01:35.495 --> 01:42.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
