The Dow Jones
industrial average rose 28
points to close

03:09.489 --> 03:17.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
at 16016. The Nasdaq was down 11
points, and
the S&amp;P 500 added just one
point.

03:17.898 --> 03:22.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Still to come on the "NewsHour":
the Supreme
Court to review President
Obama's actions

03:22.536 --> 03:29.943 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to block deportations; the lead
U.S. negotiator
on the Iranian prisoner swap;
dark clouds

03:29.976 --> 03:40.020 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on the horizon for the global
economy; and
much more.

03:40.020 --> 03:46.660 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on the horizon for the global
