June. That's the
regular schedule at the court.

09:35.442 --> 09:40.113 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If there is a decision in June,
as you well
know and we all know, that's in
the middle

09:40.146 --> 09:46.286 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the election cycle, and
immigration is
already a huge, contentious
issue. The court

09:46.319 --> 09:50.723 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
itself now becomes a player in
that very contentious
debate.

09:50.757 --> 09:52.826 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Marcia Coyle, we
thank you.

09:52.859 --> 09:54.894 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARCIA COYLE: My pleasure, Judy.

09:54.928 --> 10:01.701 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And now, for two
opposing perspectives
on this case, Marielena is the
executive director

10:01.734 --> 10:07.507 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
