up?

10:24.290 --> 10:26.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARIELENA HINCAPIE, Executive
Director, National
Immigration Law Center: Thanks,
Judy.

10:26.092 --> 10:31.064 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We definitely welcome this
