21:02.094 --> 21:03.095 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
going to say so.

21:03.129 --> 21:05.231 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BRETT MCGURK: Well, not quite.

21:05.264 --> 21:10.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hekmati was sentenced to death
in 2011. And
