to all the information that we
have. And I

21:34.093 --> 21:37.563 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
think, had we not been able to
find a way
forward here, I think these
Americans were

21:37.596 --> 21:42.201 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
looking at a very substantial,
many, many
years in Evin prison.

21:42.234 --> 21:47.072 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Why do you think
you were successful?
What were the forces inside Iran
that made

21:47.106 --> 21:49.008 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
this work, working with you?

21:49.041 --> 21:55.147 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRETT MCGURK: This process came
out of the
nuclear negotiation, but in the
nuclear negotiations,

21:55.181 --> 21:59.318 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
primarily, the Ministry of
Foreign Affairs
