Iranian system

21:59.351 --> 22:03.956 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
that don't have the
decision-making authority
over the security apparatus and
the people

22:03.989 --> 22:06.358 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that actually hold the keys to
the prison
cells.

22:06.392 --> 22:12.398 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So we had to open up a parallel
track and
begin negotiations with those
elements of

22:12.431 --> 22:19.138 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
