substantial engagement we really
ever had

22:23.275 --> 22:25.411 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
with that element of the system.

22:25.444 --> 22:29.014 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think my Iranian counterpart,
