any ground about their history
of hostage-taking

22:45.497 --> 22:50.369 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and support for terrorism, and
they would
go through their narrative.

22:50.402 --> 22:55.541 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
