course, they're
wrongfully detained, and we have
made that

24:57.029 --> 25:02.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
clear consistently, particularly
with the
Iranians. These were totally
unjust detentions,

25:02.034 --> 25:03.836 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
imprisonments.

25:03.869 --> 25:09.041 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
