the next supreme leader.

26:45.704 --> 26:49.508 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, you will have a very high
turnout. And,
already, you can see what's
happening with

26:49.541 --> 26:53.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the supreme leader trying to ban
a number
of reformist candidates. So,
within Iran,

26:53.679 --> 26:59.151 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
there is this big competition
for the reins
of power. And how that plays out
I think will

26:59.184 --> 27:00.886 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
say a lot about what's possible.

27:00.919 --> 27:04.022 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
But that's something the
Iranians have to
figure out. The United States
will continue

27:04.056 --> 27:08.360 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to protect our interests in the
region. We
define our interest based upon
our own national

27:08.393 --> 27:12.064 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
security interests. And when it
comes to Americans
sitting in Evin prison, I think
that's something

27:12.097 --> 27:14.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that we have taken with the
utmost seriousness.

27:14.399 --> 27:20.739 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, obviously, other than the
families, we
didn't tell anybody about this
channel, because,

27:20.772 --> 27:24.443 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
had it not been secret, it would
have been
impossible to make any progress.

27:24.476 --> 27:29.248 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Special
Presidential Envoy
Brett McGurk, thank you very
much.

27:29.281 --> 27:37.422 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BRETT MCGURK: Judy, thank you.

27:37.456 --> 27:41.727 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Stay with us.

27:41.760 --> 27:47.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Coming up on the "NewsHour":
