rate to slow
down.

28:47.859 --> 28:49.695 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: They wanted it?

28:49.728 --> 28:53.832 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KENNETH LIEBERTHAL: They wanted
it. The question
is, can they use this slowdown
to transition

28:53.865 --> 28:58.236 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
