47:44.762 --> 47:48.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLES NELSON: Millions and
millions and
millions of brain connections
are being built.

47:48.399 --> 47:53.938 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And so as we build the
scaffolding for subsequent
learning in those first few
